review_blob: An absoloute delight........ALTHOUGH the hangover is insane.  Keep the asprin handy for the morning.
Another beer that can be included in the serious session list.  Breaks up the lager and placed right can really prolong your drinking over a night.
This is a fantastic beer to get the night started.  Once cold, they will go down so easy.  This is my favourite beer for sinking before going out.  Very pleasant.
